Help Type: topic
Topic: recipe

Recipes

Import Markdown into an archive:
  spinedigest import notes.sdpub ./notes.md --input-format markdown

Import EPUB into an archive:
  spinedigest import book.sdpub ./book.epub

Check readiness:
  spinedigest status book.sdpub
  spinedigest index book.sdpub

Estimate a full ready build:
  spinedigest estimate book.sdpub --stage ready

Build one chapter graph:
  spinedigest build book.sdpub --stage graph --chapter 3 --confirm

Find and read source-backed knowledge:
  spinedigest find book.sdpub "knowledge graph"
  spinedigest page book.sdpub node:84

List archive objects as JSON:
  spinedigest list book.sdpub --type node --json
  spinedigest list book.sdpub --type node --chapter 3 --json
  spinedigest find book.sdpub "RAG" --json

Read one chapter as continuous text:
  spinedigest read book.sdpub chapter:3

Export a Markdown projection:
  spinedigest export book.sdpub --output-format markdown --output digest.md

Pipe Markdown into an archive:
  cat article.md | spinedigest import article.sdpub --input-format markdown

Pipe plain text into an archive:
  cat chapter.txt | spinedigest import chapter.sdpub --input-format txt

Pipe extracted webpage text into an archive:
  curl -L https://example.com/post | defuddle | spinedigest import article.sdpub --input-format markdown

One-shot stream digest:
  cat chapter.txt | spinedigest transform --input-format txt --output-format markdown
